ces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同女人講嘢千祈唔好用理性諗法<br />\n啫係你永遠當佢係有精神病嘅人<br />\n用理解 耐心同佢講嘢 <br />\n唔好要求佢做更多就得<br />\n<br />\n女人個腦永遠唔係佢自己的<br />\n永遠都俾所謂 荷爾蒙影響 大上大落 諗嘢無邏輯<br />\n<br />\n做唔到真係唔好拍拖 會好辛苦的<br />\n尤其而家廿一世紀 群魔亂舞嘅時代"},{"pid":"03269c603d0b81630f85d8cc49c8f382508bb2ab","tid":895290,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:55:11.000Z","msg":"小朋友去咩旅行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3af3b54206d45b583c63b1c35ed5e2a55f5fc0","tid":895290,"uid":209678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86c08c440bd2dd179ebb1d47722aaf82cd2e8207","tid":895290,"uid":217336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"肯定你地廿歲都未夠<br />\n你俾晒錢已經唔啱喇，重點係港女唔會理你係咪俾晒錢都好都會照發你脾氣，下次唔好咁傻豬喇，對住港女俾晒錢都唔係大晒架，你有哩個思想已經係錯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:56:16.000Z","msg":"我都係唔想佢辛苦嘛，留返啲錢買自己中意既野"},{"pid":"ad7bd18eaee2754b2c2483705e5dc65cfc419e9f","tid":895290,"uid":5912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce8e4999efcb95061b8e9726c34ed3e599662f01","tid":895290,"uid":18720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"小朋友就唔好充大頭鬼啦<br />\n學人出埋條女嗰但又窮到要做狗先捱返嚟<br />\n條女又閪 有問題唔撚溝通 又唔解決<br />\n到爆煲嗰時就屌鳩第個<br />\n<br />\n屌 好撚弱智呀<br />\n佢兩條智障做乜都嘈嫁啦<br />\n咁就會引申到同女朋友去旅行=一定鬧交？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class